{% comment %}
============================================================
  PRODUCT LUXURY — Página de producto con lógica dinámica
  de variantes, stock e integración AJAX con el carrito
============================================================
  Descripción:
  Plantilla de página de producto para Shopify con galería
  de imágenes (imagen principal + miniaturas clickeables),
  selector de variantes (talla/color) sincronizado con
  JavaScript, badge de stock en tiempo real (disponible /
  pocas unidades / agotado), botón de "agregar al carrito"
  mediante AJAX (sin recargar la página), y botón de
  WhatsApp de confianza para resolver dudas antes de comprar.

  Tecnologías: Liquid, JavaScript (vanilla, Fetch API),
  CSS3 (animaciones, responsive, grid layout), Shopify
  Object Model (product, variants, options), Shopify
  Cart AJAX API (/cart/add.js, /cart.js).

  Puntos técnicos destacados:
    - Inyección de datos de Shopify (variantes, disponibilidad,
      inventario) desde Liquid a un array de JavaScript para
      manipularlos del lado del cliente sin nuevas peticiones.
    - Sincronización de selección de variante (radio buttons)
      con el precio, disponibilidad y stock mostrado, sin
      recargar la página.
    - Uso de Fetch API para agregar productos al carrito de
      forma asíncrona, con manejo de estados de carga, éxito
      y error.
    - Emisión de un evento personalizado (CustomEvent) para
      notificar al resto del tema (Shopify Horizon) que el
      carrito cambió, y actualización manual de contadores
      de carrito en el header como respaldo.
    - Ajuste automático del máximo de cantidad disponible
      según el inventario real de la variante seleccionada.
============================================================
{% endcomment %}

<section class="luxury-product">

  <div class="luxury-container">

    <div class="luxury-image-wrapper">
      <div class="luxury-image">
        <img id="mainProductImage"
             src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 900 }}"
             alt="{{ product.title }}">
      </div>
      <div class="luxury-thumbnails">
        {% for image in product.images %}
            <img src="{{ image | image_url: width: 200 }}"
                data-large="{{ image | image_url: width: 900 }}"
                class="thumbnail"
                onclick="changeImage(this)"
                alt="">
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="luxury-info">

      <div class="luxury-stock-badge" id="stockBadge">
        <span class="stock-dot" id="stockDot"></span>
        <span id="stockText">Cargando...</span>
      </div>

      <span class="luxury-eyebrow">Colección DÉSIR</span>
      <h1 class="luxury-title">{{ product.title }}</h1>

      <div class="luxury-price-wrapper">
        {% if product.compare_at_price > product.price %}
            <span class="luxury-compare-price">{{ product.compare_at_price | money }}</span>
        {% endif %}
        <span class="luxury-price">{{ product.price | money }}</span>
      </div>

      <div class="luxury-divider"></div>

      {% form 'product', product %}

        <input type="hidden" name="id" value="{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}">

        {% unless product.has_only_default_variant %}
          {% for option in product.options_with_values %}
            <div class="luxury-option">
              <label class="luxury-option-title">{{ option.name }}</label>
              <div class="luxury-variants">
                {% for value in option.values %}
                  <label class="variant-button">
                    <input type="radio"
                           name="options[{{ option.name }}]"
                           value="{{ value }}"
                           {% if option.selected_value == value %}checked{% endif %}>
                    <span>{{ value }}</span>
                  </label>
                {% endfor %}
              </div>
            </div>
          {% endfor %}
        {% endunless %}

        <div class="luxury-quantity">
          <input type="number" name="quantity" id="quantityInput" value="1" min="1" step="1">
        </div>

        <div class="luxury-no-stock-msg" id="noStockMsg">
          En este momento no tenemos el producto disponible en esta variante.
        </div>

        <div class="luxury-cart-message"></div>

        <div class="luxury-buttons">
          <button type="submit" name="add" class="luxury-btn-primary" id="addToCartBtn">
            Agregar al carrito
          </button>
          <div class="luxury-buy-now" id="buyNowWrapper">
            {{ form | payment_button }}
          </div>
        </div>

      {% endform %}

      <a href="https://wa.me/{{ section.settings.whatsapp_number }}"
         target="_blank"
         class="luxury-whatsapp-trust">
        <span class="lwt-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path fill="currentColor" d="M16.04 2c-7.73 0-14 6.27-14 14 0 2.6.71 5.04 1.94 7.13L2 30l6.99-1.93c2.02 1.13 4.36 1.79 6.85 1.79h.01c7.73 0 14-6.27 14-14s-6.27-13.86-13.8-13.86zm0 25.6c-2.27 0-4.4-.62-6.22-1.78l-.45-.27-4.63 1.28 1.24-4.51-.29-.46a11.6 11.6 0 0 1-1.78-6.22c0-6.41 5.22-11.62 11.63-11.62 6.41 0 11.63 5.21 11.63 11.62 0 6.41-5.22 11.62-11.63 11.96zm6.43-8.71c-.35-.18-2.08-1.03-2.4-1.14-.32-.12-.56-.18-.79.18-.23.35-.91 1.14-1.12 1.37-.21.23-.41.26-.76.09-2.05-1.03-3.39-1.83-4.74-4.16-.36-.62.36-.58.99-1.93.11-.23.05-.42-.06-.6-.11-.18-.79-1.9-1.08-2.54-.29-.62-.59-.53-.81-.54-.21-.01-.45-.01-.69-.01-.24 0-.62.09-.95.45-.32.35-1.24 1.21-1.24 2.95 0 1.74 1.27 3.42 1.45 3.66.18.23 2.46 3.78 6.04 5.14 3.58 1.36 3.58.91 4.23.85.65-.06 2.08-.85 2.37-1.67.29-.82.29-1.52.2-1.67-.09-.15-.32-.24-.67-.42z"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <span class="lwt-text">{{ section.settings.whatsapp_message }}</span>
        <span class="lwt-arrow">›</span>
      </a>

      <div class="luxury-description">
        {{ product.description }}
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="lp-orb lp-orb--1"></div>

</section>

<style>

@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;1,400;1,600&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Cinzel:wght@400;600&display=swap');

.luxury-product {
  background: #0e0a0a;
  padding: 150px 40px 80px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease forwards;
}

.lp-orb {
  position: absolute;
  border-radius: 50%;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
}

.lp-orb--1 {
  width: 700px;
  height: 700px;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(161,18,42,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
  top: -200px;
  left: -150px;
}

.luxury-container {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 80px;
  align-items: start;
}

.luxury-image-wrapper {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
}

.luxury-image {
  background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1a1010, #130c0c);
  padding: 30px;
  border-radius: 35px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  border: 1px solid rgba(200,145,58,0.2);
  box-shadow:
    0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5),
    inset 0 1px 0 rgba(200,145,58,0.15);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.luxury-image::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 10%;
  right: 10%;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(200,145,58,0.5), transparent);
}

.luxury-image img {
  width: 85%;
  border-radius: 25px;
  box-shadow:
    0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5),
    0 0 30px rgba(161,18,42,0.15);
  transition: 0.4s ease;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 20px 40px rgba(161,18,42,0.2));
}

.luxury-image img:hover {
  transform: translateY(-15px);
  filter: drop-shadow(0 30px 50px rgba(161,18,42,0.3));
}

.luxury-thumbnails {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  margin-top: 20px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: center;
}

.thumbnail {
  width: 80px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: 0.3s ease;
  border: 1px solid rgba(200,145,58,0.15);
  opacity: 0.7;
}

.thumbnail:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  border-color: rgba(200,145,58,0.5);
  opacity: 1;
  box-shadow:
    0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.4),
    0 0 0 1px rgba(200,145,58,0.2),
    0 0 12px rgba(200,145,58,0.15);
}

.luxury-info {
  background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1a1010, #130c0c);
  padding: 45px;
  border-radius: 30px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(200,145,58,0.22);
  box-shadow:
    0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5),
    inset 0 1px 0 rgba(200,145,58,0.15),
    inset 0 0 60px rgba(161,18,42,0.04);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.luxury-info::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 8%;
  right: 8%;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(200,145,58,0.55), transparent);
}

.luxury-info::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 8%;
  right: 8%;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #A1122A, #c8913a, #A1122A, transparent);
  opacity: 0.5;
}

.luxury-stock-badge {
  position: absolute;
  top: 20px;
  right: 20px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 7px;
  background: rgba(14,10,10,0.75);
  border: 1px solid rgba(200,145,58,0.2);
  border-radius: 999px;
  padding: 6px 14px;
  font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: rgba(240,232,228,0.75);
  letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
  transition: all 0.4s ease;
  z-index: 10;
}

.stock-dot {
  width: 7px;
  height: 7px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: #4caf7d;
  box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(76,175,125,0.7);
  transition: all 0.4s ease;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.stock-dot.out {
  background: #A1122A;
  box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(161,18,42,0.7);
}

.stock-dot.low {
  background: #c8913a;
  box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(200,145,58,0.7);
}

.luxury-eyebrow {
  font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 300;
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #c8913a;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.luxury-title {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 42px;
  font-weight: 400;
  font-style: italic;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  color: #f5eeea;
  text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(200,145,58,0.15);
  line-height: 1.15;
}

.luxury-price-wrapper {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 15px;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

.luxury-compare-price {
  text-decoration: line-through;
  color: rgba(240,232,228,0.3);
  font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
  font-size: 17px;
  font-weight: 300;
}

.luxury-price {
  font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
  font-size: 28px;
  color: #e8c97a;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(200,145,58,0.4);
}

.luxury-divider {
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(200,145,58,0.3), rgba(161,18,42,0.3), rgba(200,145,58,0.3), transparent);
  margin: 28px 0;
}

.luxury-option-title {
  font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-size: 11px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  display: block;
  color: #c8913a;
}

.luxury-option { margin-bottom: 28px; }

.luxury-variants {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.variant-button { cursor: pointer; }
.variant-button input { display: none; }

.variant-button span {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 10px 22px;
  border-radius: 30px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(200,145,58,0.25);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(95,14,28), rgb(161,18,42));
  color: #f0e8e4;
  font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 400;
  transition: 0.3s ease;
}

.variant-button:hover span {
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  border-color: rgba(200,145,58,0.5);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(161,18,42,0.3), 0 0 12px rgba(200,145,58,0.1);
}

.variant-button input:checked + span {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1010, #2a1515);
  color: #c8913a;
  border-color: rgba(200,145,58,0.6);
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(200,145,58,0.3), 0 0 15px rgba(200,145,58,0.1);
}

.luxury-quantity input {
  width: 80px;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(200,145,58,0.2);
  background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1f1212, #180e0e);
  color: #f0e8e4;
  font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
  font-size: 14px;
  margin: 22px 0;
  outline: none;
  transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
}

.luxury-quantity input:focus {
  border-color: rgba(200,145,58,0.45);
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(200,145,58,0.1);
}

.luxury-no-stock-msg {
  display: none;
  background: rgba(161,18,42,0.08);
  border: 1px solid rgba(161,18,42,0.3);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 14px 18px;
  font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(240,180,180,0.85);
  letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  text-align: center;
}

.luxury-buttons {
  display: flex;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-top: 10px;
}

.luxury-buttons button,
.luxury-buttons .shopify-payment-button {
  flex: 1;
}

.luxury-btn-primary,
.shopify-payment-button__button {
  width: 100%;
  height: 62px;
  padding: 0 20px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(95,14,28), rgb(161,18,42));
  color: #f5eeea;
  border: 1px solid rgba(200,145,58,0.25);
  border-radius: 40px;
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif !important;
  font-size: 11px !important;
  font-weight: 600 !important;
  letter-spacing: 3.5px !important;
  text-transform: uppercase !important;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(161,18,42,0.3);
  text-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(200,145,58,0.35);
}

.luxury-btn-primary:hover,
.shopify-payment-button__button:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(161,18,42), rgb(200,26,26));
  border-color: rgba(200,145,58,0.5);
  box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(161,18,42,0.45), 0 0 20px rgba(200,145,58,0.15);
  letter-spacing: 4px !important;
  color: #e8c97a;
  text-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(200,145,58,0.55);
}

.luxury-btn-primary:disabled,
.luxury-btn-primary.disabled {
  opacity: 0.35;
  cursor: not-allowed;
  transform: none !important;
  box-shadow: none !important;
  letter-spacing: 3.5px !important;
}

.shopify-payment-button__button--hidden {
  display: none !important;
}

/* ---- Mensaje de confianza WhatsApp ---- */
